Feature: GitHub API

  Scenario: Using GitHub API
    Given I set User-Agent request header to veggies/1.0
    When I GET https://api.github.com/
    Then response status code should be 200
    When I pick response json emojis_url as emojisUrl
    And I GET {{emojisUrl}}
    Then response status code should be 200

